      <scopecontent id="aspace_76993e7f7a43cc5d37c446f6e2779e53">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The motion pictures document the construction of Sterling Memorial Library, Yale University, and the procession of books and move of the library from the Old Library (now Dwight Hall) to Sterling Memorial Library.</p>  
